Interface Event3Delegate<T1,​T2,​T3>

  • Type Parameters:
    T1 - The type of the first information parameter the event provides
    T2 - The type of the second information parameter the event provides
    T3 - The type of the third information parameter the event provides

    Action3<T1,​T2,​T3>, Event3<T1,​T2,​T3>
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Event3Delegate<T1,​T2,​T3>
extends Action3<T1,​T2,​T3>, Event3<T1,​T2,​T3>
    An Event3Delegate implements Action3 as well as Event3 and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action3 interface to all subscribers of the Event3 interface.
